    <h3 class="article deck">"The Fault in Our Stars" author John Green wrote one of the three intertwining Christmas tales</h3>
    <div class="article copy node">

    
        <div class="related articles space out">
             <div class="article spot">
                <div id="grv-personalization-24"></div>
        <script type="text/javascript">
