  <a href="http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/gallery/broadcast-tvs-returning-shows-2014-689132">
    <img src="http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/sites/default/files/custom/untitled%20folder3/Returning_Shows_300x109.jpg">
